1
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:36,880
You Chi.

2
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:42,800
You Chi?

3
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:04,600
<i>Wu Shiguang, ever since we were kids,</i>

4
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,560
<i>I've been your little tagalong.</i>

5
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,920
<i>I was your playmate.</i>

6
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:13,240
<i>I left home with you</i>

7
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:16,480
<i>and braved danger with you.</i>

8
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:20,920
Why can't I remember it?

9
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:24,000
<i>I even followed you to the Shilin Sect.</i>

10
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:26,440
Have you seen Wu Shiguang?

11
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:28,240
I've got something really fun to tell him.

12
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:29,640
Master Dragon Deity?

13
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:32,080
He's busy. Don't bother him.

14
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:33,920
He's still got a lot to deal with.

15
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:43,000
<i>The people at the Shilin Sect</i>
<i>are all pretty nice.</i>

16
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:46,240
You little weasel,
keep that Shilin Sect token on tight.

17
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:47,920
Or you'll be wiped out.

18
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:53,360
<i>But the Shilin Sect isn't my home.</i>

19
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,880
<i>A weasel demon like me shouldn't be here.</i>

20
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:59,520
Is that the Dragon Deity?

21
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:00,560
-Look.
-He has to be.

22
00:04:00,640 --> 00:04:02,360
Even the demon hunter commander
is standing behind him.

23
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:04,520
-He has to be.
-That's right.

24
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:06,720
Exactly, he must be the Dragon Deity!

25
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:11,240
<i>Being here, I feel like I'm in a skin</i>
<i>that doesn't belong to me.</i>

26
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:12,960
<i>It's uncomfortable.</i>

27
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:19,720
-<i>Now you've got so many demon hunters</i>
-This is for you.

28
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:20,800
<i>following you.</i>

29
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:25,160
<i>Maybe you don't really need me anymore.</i>

30
00:04:36,080 --> 00:04:37,160
I need to talk to you.

31
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:40,120
Commander Li wants to see me.
Let's talk later.

32
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:24,760
<i>So,</i>

33
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:27,640
<i>I'm leaving, Wu Shiguang.</i>

34
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:34,600
You idiot weasel.

35
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:01,760
Formless Moon, hear my command.

36
00:06:05,960 --> 00:06:06,880
Go.

37
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,760
Activate the Nuwa Formation

38
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:13,120
and reveal the Four Pillars

39
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:15,160
that uphold the earth.

40
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:16,680
Yes.

41
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,520
Have you seen You Chi?

42
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:49,800
-Wangyan!
-Canyue.

43
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,000
Canyue!

44
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:54,840
Canyue.

45
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:58,040
Stop her.

46
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,000
Canyue.

47
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:17,280
Wangyan,

48
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:20,480
what happened?

49
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,320
Jiu Ying…

50
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,640
Jiu Ying isn't dead.

51
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:37,840
He possessed Wuyi.

52
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,880
<i>Do you remember</i>

53
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:49,920
<i>the four divine trees that uphold</i>
<i>the earth I told you about?</i>

54
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:52,160
<i>The Tree of Water grew beneath the sea.</i>

55
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:55,640
<i>Its trunk is now the throne</i>
<i>in Formless Moon's main hall.</i>

56
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:00,880
Go.

57
00:08:01,520 --> 00:08:02,440
Yes.

58
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:10,120
<i>The Crying Elm,</i>
<i>now reduced to a broken stump,</i>

59
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:12,200
<i>is the Tree of Earth.</i>

60
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:27,240
The Firefluff Tree hidden in the axle
of Wei mansion's weaving workshop

61
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:28,160
is the Tree of Fire.

62
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:44,200
Why does Jiu Ying want to destroy
the Four Pillars?

63
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,640
He wants the earth to collapse,

64
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:48,400
<i>all living things to perish,</i>

65
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,560
<i>and this world</i>

66
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:53,960
to be left with nothing
but fear and despair.

67
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:56,680
Where is the Tree of Metal?

68
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:02,240
The Shilin Sect's Golden Scale Tree

69
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:05,080
is the Tree of Metal.

70
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,160
Good thing

71
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:10,000
there is the Eternal Formation
keeping them away.

72
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,560
No.

73
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,240
Wuyi

74
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:18,040
has a Shilin Sect token.

75
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:21,800
TOKEN OF SCALES

76
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:52,240
Wu Shiguang, why haven't
you come to find me?

77
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:56,520
If you don't show up today,
I won't be so easy

78
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,280
to cheer up!

79
00:10:12,400 --> 00:10:13,440
Ye Changsheng,

80
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:16,840
bring the nearby townsfolk
into the Shilin Sect for protection.

81
00:10:16,920 --> 00:10:17,760
Yes.

82
00:10:20,280 --> 00:10:21,120
Hurry!

83
00:10:22,280 --> 00:10:23,440
Watch your step!

84
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:28,440
This way! Quick!

85
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:32,240
Keep up!

86
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,760
-Be careful! Hurry!
-Go!

87
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,480
SERVE THE SCALES, UPHOLD THE RIGHT

88
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:41,240
Move!

89
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:42,000
-Go!
-Keep up!

90
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,320
Inside! Go!

91
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:55,320
If the Four Pillars collapse completely,

92
00:10:56,920 --> 00:11:00,640
heaven and earth,
including the Shilin Sect, will topple.

93
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,120
We have to stop Jiu Ying,

94
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:03,800
but…

95
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:06,920
Master Dragon Deity.

96
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:27,080
My soul I devote. Long live the dragon.

97
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:37,200
Master Dragon Deity, we await your orders.

98
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,240
<i>Members of the Formless Moon</i>

99
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:48,560
<i>can draw on the elemental power</i>
<i>of the Four Pillars.</i>

100
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:52,400
<i>The possessed sisters</i>
<i>will be much stronger and hard to defeat.</i>

101
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:56,280
Only spells that counter
the pillars' elements

102
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:57,280
can oppose them.

103
00:11:58,040 --> 00:12:00,800
Mo Yuntan, your artifact,
the Spirit Brush,

104
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:03,160
uses ink-based water magic.

105
00:12:03,680 --> 00:12:04,520
It can counter fire.

106
00:12:06,560 --> 00:12:07,840
Leave the Firefluff Tree to me.

107
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:16,120
The Crying Elm is the oldest tree,

108
00:12:17,040 --> 00:12:18,000
<i>the ancestor of all trees.</i>

109
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:42,920
My artifact, Golden Resonance,
counters wood. Perfect.

110
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:53,480
My blade is a divine weapon
left behind by a mountain demon.

111
00:12:53,560 --> 00:12:55,280
For centuries, it'd drawn

112
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:57,600
on the essence of the soil
from the peak of Mount Nandang.

113
00:12:57,680 --> 00:12:58,520
<i>Earth counters water.</i>

114
00:12:58,600 --> 00:13:00,560
I'll handle the Formless Moon's
Tree of Water.

115
00:13:08,560 --> 00:13:10,280
That leaves the Golden Scale Tree.

116
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,240
Hua Qi…

117
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:13,400
What, are you going to attack your sister?

118
00:14:14,280 --> 00:14:16,680
It's Jiu Ying I'm going to strike at.

119
00:14:17,920 --> 00:14:19,480
Give my sister back!

120
00:14:54,840 --> 00:14:55,680
What happened?

121
00:14:57,560 --> 00:14:58,520
You Chi,

122
00:14:59,760 --> 00:15:01,760
-leave.
-No way.

123
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:03,480
How can I leave when you're like this?

124
00:15:04,080 --> 00:15:06,160
Hua Qi, I'm no healer.

125
00:15:06,240 --> 00:15:07,520
Is there any way I can help?

126
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,160
Yes.

127
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:10,480
Take my place

128
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:12,560
and save the Golden Scale Tree.

129
00:15:13,680 --> 00:15:15,200
Save the Golden Scale Tree?

130
00:15:15,280 --> 00:15:16,520
How?

131
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:19,360
Should I catch bugs or water it?

132
00:15:36,800 --> 00:15:39,200
Always keep this token on you.

133
00:15:39,280 --> 00:15:42,520
Otherwise, the ancient formations
all over the Shilin Sect

134
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:45,040
will reduce you to ashes in an instant.

135
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:53,000
<i>Remember.</i>

136
00:15:53,920 --> 00:15:56,920
<i>No matter what you are</i>
<i>or how capable you are,</i>

137
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:01,480
<i>always give it everything you've got,</i>
<i>and do your best.</i>

138
00:16:02,440 --> 00:16:04,080
<i>Only then can you have no regrets.</i>

139
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:17,040
A little weasel thinks
he can fight a nine-tailed fox?

140
00:16:21,440 --> 00:16:22,520
Haven't you heard?

141
00:16:23,920 --> 00:16:25,160
Fire counters metal.

142
00:16:26,160 --> 00:16:27,440
Hua Qi,

143
00:16:28,640 --> 00:16:30,720
you're draining your power.

144
00:16:30,800 --> 00:16:33,160
Almost done, Master Dragon Deity.

145
00:16:34,280 --> 00:16:35,440
Hold on a little longer.

146
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:47,280
Wangyan!

147
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:56,320
Wangyan,

148
00:16:57,320 --> 00:17:01,040
did you think I couldn't beat you?

149
00:17:50,080 --> 00:17:50,960
<i>Shiguang.</i>

150
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:55,200
You are the only one in this world
I still can't let go of.

151
00:17:55,840 --> 00:17:57,280
Though I am gone,

152
00:17:57,800 --> 00:17:59,360
the Star Stone remains.

153
00:18:00,040 --> 00:18:01,400
If you find yourself
in dire straits one day,

154
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:03,640
it may yet help you once.

155
00:18:04,520 --> 00:18:05,720
But remember this.

156
00:18:06,360 --> 00:18:08,200
The Star Stone's power is too great.

157
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:09,960
Do not use it rashly.

158
00:18:10,040 --> 00:18:11,000
Master…

159
00:18:12,320 --> 00:18:13,400
<i>"Heaven and earth tremble.</i>

160
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:15,080
<i>Chaos fills the world.</i>

161
00:18:15,160 --> 00:18:16,680
<i>An old soul returns against time.</i>

162
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:19,240
<i>A new moon reshapes the world."</i>

163
00:18:19,320 --> 00:18:20,640
"Heaven and earth tremble.

164
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:22,840
Chaos fills the world."

165
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:26,280
The last share
of Chi Wen's Dragon Deity's Power

166
00:18:26,960 --> 00:18:28,240
took Ji Ling's heart stone

167
00:18:28,320 --> 00:18:30,200
to the Dragon Abyss.

168
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,680
Perhaps thousands of years from now,

169
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:34,600
it may take human form.

170
00:18:35,600 --> 00:18:37,040
"An old soul returns against time."

171
00:18:39,400 --> 00:18:40,400
"An old soul returns against time."

172
00:18:40,920 --> 00:18:41,960
Hua Qi.

173
00:18:44,880 --> 00:18:45,960
Go to the Dragon Abyss.

174
00:18:51,200 --> 00:18:52,280
Give me your hand.

175
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:57,440
Go to the Dragon Abyss.

176
00:18:57,520 --> 00:18:59,880
Use my blood to activate
the Star Stone illusion

177
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:02,880
and bring Ji Ling's heart stone inside.

178
00:19:03,400 --> 00:19:04,600
Go, now.

179
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:05,760
All right.

180
00:19:28,240 --> 00:19:29,280
This…

181
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:31,480
isn't my limit yet.

182
00:19:38,800 --> 00:19:40,440
Do my best

183
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:43,400
and leave no regrets!

184
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:49,640
You only know fire counters metal.

185
00:19:50,640 --> 00:19:54,080
But do you know that ice counters fire?

186
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:26,400
A fleeting moment in the mortal world

187
00:21:26,920 --> 00:21:28,280
is a thousand years in the illusion.

188
00:21:28,800 --> 00:21:32,520
Master Dragon Deity,
I will bring Ji Ling back.

189
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:45,720
Your weapon's gone,
and you still won't give up?

190
00:21:45,800 --> 00:21:47,000
The blade's gone,

191
00:21:48,440 --> 00:21:49,560
but I'm still here.

192
00:21:49,640 --> 00:21:51,920
Today, I am going to defeat you!

193
00:22:05,640 --> 00:22:06,640
Who says

194
00:22:07,520 --> 00:22:08,680
a weasel

195
00:22:09,520 --> 00:22:10,880
can't beat a nine-tailed fox?

196
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:25,960
Wu Shiguang,

197
00:22:28,040 --> 00:22:28,960
this time,

198
00:22:31,120 --> 00:22:33,080
I… I didn't

199
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:36,200
hold you back.

200
00:22:44,680 --> 00:22:45,800
You'd better not

201
00:22:47,200 --> 00:22:50,200
lock me inside the Cosmic Pouch again.

202
00:25:20,120 --> 00:25:21,160
"An old soul…"

203
00:25:23,760 --> 00:25:25,080
THE OLD DRAGON FALLS
THE NEW DRAGON RISES

204
00:25:25,160 --> 00:25:26,280
<i>"Returns against time."</i>

205
00:25:29,880 --> 00:25:30,720
You're back.

206
00:25:31,800 --> 00:25:32,920
I am.

207
00:25:34,400 --> 00:25:35,280
And

208
00:25:36,920 --> 00:25:38,240
so are they.

209
00:26:01,760 --> 00:26:02,760
Master.

210
00:26:23,040 --> 00:26:24,440
Why are you all back?

211
00:26:24,960 --> 00:26:27,440
Because Ji Ling has already
awakened the people

212
00:26:27,960 --> 00:26:29,040
of the Formless Moon.

213
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:32,160
Wake.

214
00:28:27,240 --> 00:28:28,280
Wang,

215
00:28:29,320 --> 00:28:33,040
the Four Pillars have been corrupted
by the evil energy inside Jiu Ying.

216
00:28:34,560 --> 00:28:37,520
Only by sacrificing
the Formless Moon power within us

217
00:28:38,240 --> 00:28:40,440
can we cleanse that evil energy.

218
00:28:41,120 --> 00:28:43,120
The wrong was ours.

219
00:28:43,960 --> 00:28:46,080
Let us make amends ourselves.

220
00:28:46,680 --> 00:28:50,080
Wang, we leave the rest to you.

221
00:28:50,840 --> 00:28:52,000
<i>Save this world</i>

222
00:28:52,520 --> 00:28:54,760
<i>we have guarded for a millennium.</i>

223
00:28:59,000 --> 00:28:59,920
What is it?

224
00:29:01,000 --> 00:29:02,360
What did the Moon Summoning Pearl say?

225
00:29:03,560 --> 00:29:04,520
Nothing.

226
00:29:05,160 --> 00:29:07,360
The sisters have all come to their senses.

227
00:29:09,280 --> 00:29:10,840
They're repairing the Four Pillars.

228
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:16,120
The collapse has stopped.

229
00:29:17,480 --> 00:29:19,720
Looks like they're all restored.

230
00:29:53,080 --> 00:29:54,160
I'll check on the Golden Scale Tree.

231
00:29:54,240 --> 00:29:55,760
Be careful.

232
00:29:56,480 --> 00:29:57,320
I've got it covered here.

233
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:25,760
You're still alive?

234
00:30:26,280 --> 00:30:29,560
Too bad Lu Wuyi thought
you were truly dead.

235
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:31,200
She was so heartbroken

236
00:30:32,120 --> 00:30:35,080
that even her soul scattered into nothing.

237
00:30:36,160 --> 00:30:37,120
Jiu Ying,

238
00:30:38,160 --> 00:30:39,600
you killed Wu.

239
00:30:41,320 --> 00:30:42,320
Today,

240
00:30:43,080 --> 00:30:45,520
I will make sure
your soul is utterly destroyed.

241
00:30:59,280 --> 00:31:00,320
Lu Wuyi,

242
00:31:01,560 --> 00:31:03,680
you woke up again?

243
00:31:03,760 --> 00:31:04,960
I told you,

244
00:31:06,520 --> 00:31:08,120
the one who should get out

245
00:31:09,360 --> 00:31:10,680
is you.

246
00:31:14,080 --> 00:31:14,960
Wu.

247
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:19,600
Ji,

248
00:31:20,960 --> 00:31:23,440
Jiu Ying has been trying to take control.

249
00:31:24,640 --> 00:31:25,600
Ji,

250
00:31:26,680 --> 00:31:27,640
do it.

251
00:31:28,720 --> 00:31:29,920
Kill me.

252
00:31:35,120 --> 00:31:37,480
Since I was created, I've been controlled

253
00:31:38,440 --> 00:31:39,640
my whole life.

254
00:31:41,840 --> 00:31:43,200
This time,

255
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:47,200
I want to be my true self.

256
00:31:49,640 --> 00:31:50,760
Help me,

257
00:31:52,320 --> 00:31:53,400
Ji.

258
00:32:09,480 --> 00:32:10,320
Form up.

259
00:32:13,400 --> 00:32:14,240
Qisha of the Southern Dipper.

260
00:32:14,320 --> 00:32:15,320
Tiantong of the Southern Dipper.

261
00:32:15,400 --> 00:32:16,440
Pojun of the Northern Dipper.

262
00:32:16,520 --> 00:32:17,400
In positions!

263
00:34:39,520 --> 00:34:40,360
Master.

264
00:35:05,320 --> 00:35:06,240
You Chi.

265
00:35:06,920 --> 00:35:07,880
Wangyan,

266
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:09,520
I did great

267
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:12,080
this time.

268
00:35:14,160 --> 00:35:15,320
She said

269
00:35:15,400 --> 00:35:16,800
a weasel

270
00:35:17,720 --> 00:35:19,080
couldn't beat a nine-tailed fox,

271
00:35:19,600 --> 00:35:21,760
but look,

272
00:35:23,320 --> 00:35:24,880
I still beat her.

273
00:35:29,520 --> 00:35:31,560
I helped, didn't I?

274
00:35:32,080 --> 00:35:33,160
Oh, right.

275
00:35:33,720 --> 00:35:34,680
Look.

276
00:35:35,360 --> 00:35:36,280
I was

277
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:39,480
so smart this time.

278
00:35:41,760 --> 00:35:43,000
Wu Shiguang

279
00:35:43,080 --> 00:35:45,480
won't get to call me an idiot again.

280
00:35:46,920 --> 00:35:48,040
Do you know?

281
00:35:48,640 --> 00:35:50,800
Wu Shiguang always says

282
00:35:51,400 --> 00:35:53,120
that when danger comes,

283
00:35:54,840 --> 00:35:57,200
I'm the type to dig a hole and hide in it.

284
00:35:57,280 --> 00:35:59,200
Before you came,

285
00:35:59,960 --> 00:36:01,600
I was so sad,

286
00:36:02,720 --> 00:36:05,200
because I was going to die here alone,

287
00:36:06,680 --> 00:36:08,120
and no one would ever know.

288
00:36:09,640 --> 00:36:10,800
Wu Shiguang

289
00:36:11,640 --> 00:36:13,720
must think I ran away again.

290
00:36:17,160 --> 00:36:18,400
Oh, right.

291
00:36:19,000 --> 00:36:20,880
Remember to tell him

292
00:36:21,440 --> 00:36:22,600
that I…

293
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:25,160
I really…

294
00:36:27,120 --> 00:36:30,400
really did my best. I did…

295
00:36:31,840 --> 00:36:33,560
I did my best.

296
00:36:37,240 --> 00:36:39,200
You Chi. You Chi!

297
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:22,320
How?

298
00:38:23,040 --> 00:38:25,640
Lu Wuyi's soul was unusually resilient.

299
00:38:26,160 --> 00:38:28,640
I was never able to find a way
to erase it completely.

300
00:38:29,240 --> 00:38:31,680
I should thank you, Wu Shiguang.

301
00:38:31,760 --> 00:38:33,920
With your Dragon Deity's Power,

302
00:38:34,440 --> 00:38:37,240
you wiped out the last trace of her soul

303
00:38:37,760 --> 00:38:40,640
and let me own this body completely.

304
00:38:44,080 --> 00:38:46,560
Why won't Lu Wuyi's body die?

305
00:38:49,400 --> 00:38:50,680
HEAVEN AND EARTH TREMBLE
CHAOS FILLS THE WORLD

306
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:52,040
AN OLD SOUL RETURNS AGAINST TIME
A NEW MOON RESHAPES THE WORLD

307
00:38:54,080 --> 00:38:55,520
<i>The Oracle Stone is missing a piece.</i>

308
00:38:55,600 --> 00:38:57,080
The Oracle Stone!

309
00:38:57,160 --> 00:39:00,240
Besides a fragment of Jiu Ying's spirit,

310
00:39:00,960 --> 00:39:03,040
a fragment of the Oracle Stone
is in her too.

311
00:39:05,120 --> 00:39:06,480
Wu's body

312
00:39:06,560 --> 00:39:09,520
was made from the flesh
and blood of nine-tailed foxes.

313
00:39:09,600 --> 00:39:13,040
It has the power of rebirth
granted by the Formless Moon.

314
00:39:13,760 --> 00:39:17,040
If she also has the Oracle Stone's
ever-living divine power,

315
00:39:18,200 --> 00:39:19,080
then…

316
00:39:24,200 --> 00:39:25,960
Is there really no other way?

317
00:39:28,480 --> 00:39:30,120
"An old soul returns against time.

318
00:39:31,680 --> 00:39:33,360
A new moon reshapes the world."

319
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:38,000
A new moon…

320
00:39:49,720 --> 00:39:51,320
There is still one way.

321
00:39:53,840 --> 00:39:55,280
And it's the only way.

322
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:00,320
You've thought of it too.

323
00:40:01,640 --> 00:40:02,880
What is it?

324
00:40:05,800 --> 00:40:07,280
Turn back time

325
00:40:07,840 --> 00:40:09,240
and go back to the past

326
00:40:10,920 --> 00:40:13,120
to stop Lu Wuyi from ever being born.

327
00:40:13,840 --> 00:40:14,920
In other words,

328
00:40:16,440 --> 00:40:18,840
erase Lu Wuyi's existence completely.

329
00:40:24,680 --> 00:40:26,640
Didn't Lonescale tell you?

330
00:40:27,680 --> 00:40:30,640
The recent past of a few days
can be changed.

331
00:40:31,760 --> 00:40:34,320
But Lu Wuyi was born 50 years ago.

332
00:40:35,280 --> 00:40:39,480
To go back that far and change the past?

333
00:40:41,320 --> 00:40:42,760
A fool's dream.

334
00:40:44,680 --> 00:40:46,200
"A new moon reshapes the world."

335
00:40:46,720 --> 00:40:50,160
Since the Oracle Stone
gave such a prophecy,

336
00:40:50,960 --> 00:40:52,360
it means

337
00:40:55,040 --> 00:40:56,840
this is destined to happen.

338
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:01,800
I was a fallen star
from beyond the heavens.

339
00:41:02,960 --> 00:41:04,920
I'm not bound by the laws of this world.

340
00:41:08,560 --> 00:41:10,200
There was one question

341
00:41:11,000 --> 00:41:12,760
I spent my whole life pondering.

342
00:41:13,760 --> 00:41:17,480
Even after bitter years of cultivation,
I could never solve it.

343
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:20,680
You bear extraordinary power
from beyond the heavens.

344
00:41:20,760 --> 00:41:23,960
Slaughter is not your only choice.

345
00:41:24,560 --> 00:41:26,400
I hope that one day,

346
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:28,840
you'll find the true meaning
of coming to this world

347
00:41:28,920 --> 00:41:30,880
after crossing

348
00:41:31,400 --> 00:41:32,720
countless galaxies.

349
00:41:33,800 --> 00:41:36,040
For the past thousand years,
I have asked myself

350
00:41:38,040 --> 00:41:40,720
why I came to this world

351
00:41:41,800 --> 00:41:42,840
and what

352
00:41:44,880 --> 00:41:46,800
I could do for it.

353
00:41:48,280 --> 00:41:49,720
Now I understand.

354
00:41:51,640 --> 00:41:55,160
After I crossed the galaxies
and came to this world,

355
00:41:56,280 --> 00:41:57,680
I brought disaster upon it

356
00:41:58,280 --> 00:41:59,960
and gave rise to Jiu Ying.

357
00:42:04,120 --> 00:42:05,160
So,

358
00:42:06,720 --> 00:42:08,920
it should be me who brings him to an end

359
00:42:10,160 --> 00:42:11,920
and saves this world.

